snippet.title: Super Scramble Simulator
snippet.description:
Available on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2363510/Super_Scramble_Simulator_AmigaC64CPCSpectrum/?curator_clanid=38465691

Originally released in 1989, this dirtbike simulator brought all the fun and challenge of motocross to home computers. Now, relive those days in this remastered emulated version.

Contains all the versions originally created for the Amiga, Commodore 64, Amstrad CPC, and ZX Spectrum computers.
